# This directory holds the FAISS index built by ingest.py.
# The index files (index.faiss, index.pkl) are excluded from version control
# because they are ~8 MB binary artefacts that can be regenerated.
#
# To build the index locally:
#   cd LangChainService
#   EMBEDDING_URL=http://localhost:8001/embed python ingest.py
#
# See Data/README.md for the full regeneration workflow.
